000700 01  WS-Y             PIC 9(3) VALUE ZEROS.
000800*
000900 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
001000 MAIN-PARA.
001100     MOVE 10 TO WS-X.
001200     MOVE 20 TO WS-Y.
001300*    Test nested IF: X < Y and Y > 15
001400     IF WS-X < WS-Y
001500         IF WS-Y > 15
001600             DISPLAY "X<Y AND Y>15"
001700         ELSE
001800             DISPLAY "X<Y AND Y<=15"
001900         END-IF
002000     ELSE
002100         DISPLAY "X>=Y"
002200     END-IF.
002300*    Test with reversed values
002400     MOVE 20 TO WS-X.
002500     MOVE 5 TO WS-Y.
002600     IF WS-X < WS-Y
002700         DISPLAY "SHOULD NOT PRINT"
002800     ELSE
002900         IF WS-Y < 10
003000             DISPLAY "X>=Y AND Y<10"
003100         ELSE
003200             DISPLAY "X>=Y AND Y>=10"
003300         END-IF
003400     END-IF.
003500*    Test equality
